venue.name: Antica Pizzeria e Friggitoria dal Presidente
Cappella Del Tesoro Di San Gennaro

tip.text: Magnificent seafood, primi Trocolli special had the softest octopus I have ever had, Special ambience and very friendly service, worth going out of the way.
Brilliant food, the tuna and swordfish and home made ravioli were melt in your mouth with great sauces, very friendly staff and their kids helped out as well.
Great bar for evening drinks, staff are very friendly with Mimo being the standout..try the artisan beers they are excellent, especially the local Italian. Good selfie mirror as well..😂😂😂
